    <gsw_content_information action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE">
        <active>true</active>
        <article><![CDATA[<p>Set the <em>x_taniu_tan_core.tanium_module_api_url</em> system property to the URL or IP Address of your Tanium Server (including HTTPS) PLUS the API path prefix (e.g. &#34;/plugin/products&#34;). This will typically be very similar to the Tanium API Endpoint property [<em>x_13231_tan_jit_ds.tanium_api_endpoint</em>]. <br />When this property is used for an API call, the module name, API version, and API method name will be appended automatically to the value of this property (e.g. &#34;/deploy/v1/api_method_name&#34; for Deploy).</p>
<p><strong>Example</strong>: <em>https://i-abc123.i.labspace.tanium.com/plugin/products or https://192.168.7.193/plugin/products</em></p>]]></article>
